title: Mr. Robot Complete Season 1
description:
Complete 1st Season of Mr. Robot.  I believe all or most of these are ettv uploads originally, so please understand I didn't encode any of these, I'm just sharing them all together so you don't have to try to hunt them down individually.  The quality will vary on a couple of episodes unfortunately, but they are all in pretty good quality, some are just better than others.  I tried to get the best download each week when it was available.  Hope you enjoy, I know I really like the show
